Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的计算 各科的失误都只在一到两处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这群家伙中肯定能拿到总分第一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个 八轩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 错了一道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 八轩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是农家的孩子 畜产能答这个分数好牛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 这没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(564,246)}畜产
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(494,340)}农作物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.81,0:00:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(562,316)}食品制造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(482,358)}农业经营
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 八轩是遥遥领先的总分第一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种不甘心！
