Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.91,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}习惯了你开车时的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:22.71,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}夏日的海风 清爽心怡的 Summer day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:22.71,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}潮風が気持ちいい Summer day
